## Regulatory change example (realistic)

### Scenario

> EU updates UBO rules

### Decision-driven response

* Update EMEA layer of `CLM-Decision-KYC`
* No Case Type change
* No flow change
* No product redeployment

### Case-type-driven response

* Multiple CT updates
* Regression across products
* Long approval cycle

